Vestas Signs New 1.3 Billion Euro Revolving Credit Facility

-- B y   G e l u   S u l u g i u c
-- 
2011-06-22T10:41:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/vestas-signs-new-1-3-billion-euro-revolving-credit-facility.html
Vestas Wind Systems A/S signed a new
1.3 billion euro revolving credit facility. Commerzbank and DnB
NOR were joint coordinators and bookrunners.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
